query:
SELECT tp.id, tp.userId, tp.approvalStatus, u.name, u.email 
FROM tutor_profiles tp 
INNER JOIN users u ON tp.userId = u.id 
ORDER BY tp.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
